            <title>[CXF-3758] when web container be redeployed WebServiceContextImpl&apos;s static atrribute ThreadLocal&lt;MessageContext&gt; may not be release successfully.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-3758</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when I redeploy cxf application in tomcat 7,I found some log indicate that  ThreadLocal&amp;lt;MessageContext&amp;gt; object may not be release successfully&#65292;When I implements GenericServlet&apos;s destroy method as follows&#65306;&lt;br/&gt;
	@Override&lt;br/&gt;
	public void destroy() &lt;/p&gt;
{
		WebServiceContextImpl.clear();
	}
&lt;p&gt;this bug been fixed&#12290;&lt;br/&gt;
there may be some other resources not be destroy as above&#12290;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
